ng.html\/#Uu_the_cua_cong_cu_Video_Marketing\" title=\"\u01afu th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 Video Marketing \">\u01afu th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 Video Marketing <\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/xu-huong-video-marketing.html\/#Suc_manh_cua_Video_Marketing\" title=\"S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Video Marketing\">S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Video Marketing<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/xu-huong-video-marketing.html\/#4_Xu_huong_Video_Marketing_dang_thinh_hanh\" title=\"4 Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng\u00a0Video Marketing\u00a0\u0111ang th\u1ecbnh h\u00e0nh \">4 Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng\u00a0Video Marketing\u00a0\u0111ang th\u1ecbnh h\u00e0nh <\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/xu-huong-video-marketing.html\/#Video_theo_trend\" title=\"Video theo &#8220;trend&#8221;\">Video theo &#8220;trend&#8221;<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/xu-huong-video-marketing.html\/#Video_am_nhac\" title=\"Video \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c\">Video \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/xu-huong-video-marketing.html\/#Video_Motion_Graphic\" title=\"Video Motion Graphic\">Video Motion Graphic<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/xu-huong-video-marketing.html\/#Video_phim_ngan\" title=\"Video phim ng\u1eafn\">Video phim ng\u1eafn<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p>H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua th\u00edch th\u00fa v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m sau khi xem xong video qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o. H\u1ecd h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u00ec n\u00f3. T\u1ea1i sao v\u1eady? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/video-marketing-la-gi.html\/\">s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Video qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/a> v\u00e0 <strong>Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng Video Marketing<\/strong> \u0111ang th\u1ecbnh h\u00e0nh nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Uu_the_cua_cong_cu_Video_Marketing\"><\/span>\u01afu th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 Video Marketing <span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Video l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u00e0 tinh t\u1ebf nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 l\u1eddi n\u00f3i. N\u00f3 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed9i dung s\u00e2u s\u1eafc v\u00e0 th\u00fa v\u1ecb m\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u1eddi n\u00f3i hay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ed9t t\u1ea3 h\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n video c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac. Video mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem nh\u1eefng cung b\u1eadc c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, l\u00fac th\u00ec c\u01b0\u1eddi ra n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, l\u00fac th\u00ec \u0111au kh\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ebfn tu\u1ed9t c\u00f9ng, l\u00fac th\u00ec h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00ed d\u1ecfm, c\u00f3 l\u00fac l\u1ea1i tr\u1ea7m l\u1eafng bi ai&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Video c\u00f3 t\u00ednh lan truy\u1ec1n nhanh v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"650\" height=\"413\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/13360VideoMarketing_1504542136.jpg\" alt=\"xu huong video marketing  \" class=\"wp-image-6673\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/13360VideoMarketing_1504542136.jpg 650w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/13360VideoMarketing_1504542136-300x191.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Suc_manh_cua_Video_Marketing\"><\/span>S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Video Marketing<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y? Khi b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm mua m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 tr\u00ean internet. V\u00ed d\u1ee5, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe \u00f4 t\u00f4 4 ch\u1ed7 v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm tr\u00ean Google bao g\u1ed3m: c\u00e1c banner qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Adwords, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng link c\u00e1c website v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t video gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 m\u1eabu xe ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p th\u00ec b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd click v\u00e0o c\u00e1i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean? K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 h\u01a1n 70% ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u1ec1u th\u00edch xem video h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua th\u00edch th\u00fa v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m sau khi xem xong video qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o. H\u1ecd h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u00ec n\u00f3. T\u1ea1i sao v\u1eady?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/maxresdefault-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Video qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o\" class=\"wp-image-6674\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/maxresdefault-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/maxresdefault-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/maxresdefault-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/maxresdefault.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u1edf tr\u00ean, video l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem. N\u00f3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a chuy\u00ean gia, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng sau khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, quy tr\u00ecnh t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m&#8230; \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u0103ng th\u00eam ni\u1ec1m tin, s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Xu_huong_Video_Marketing_dang_thinh_hanh\"><\/span>4 Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng\u00a0Video Marketing\u00a0\u0111ang th\u1ecbnh h\u00e0nh <span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Video_theo_trend\"><\/span><strong>Video theo &#8220;trend&#8221;<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1eaft trend l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi th\u1ebf. &#8220;V\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u0111i con&#8221; \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 trong mang phim chuy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i hi\u1ec7n nay. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u video qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 theo trend l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y th\u00ec ch\u1eafc ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft. Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 th\u1ee9c th\u00ec \u0111\u00e1nh v\u00e0o t\u00e2m l\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, v\u00e0 c\u00f2n g\u00ec t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u t\u1eeb trend.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/maxresdefault-8-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng Video Marketing\" class=\"wp-image-6675\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/maxresdefault-8-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/maxresdefault-8-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/maxresdefault-8-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/maxresdefault-8.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Video_am_nhac\"><\/span><strong>Video \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>\u00c2m nh\u1ea1c c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edbng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i hi\u1ec7n nay. V\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc thu\u1ed9c m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i h\u00e1t c\u0169ng nhanh h\u01a1n vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea1n ghi nh\u1edb m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u0103n. \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn b\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea1n ghi nh\u1edb m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. <strong>Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng video marketing <\/strong>n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e3n h\u00e0ng \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 n\u00f3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"573\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/qu\u1ea3ng-c\u00e1o-\u0110i\u1ec7n-M\u00e1y-Xanh-_cover-1024x573.png\" alt=\"Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng Video Marketing hi\u1ec7n nay\" class=\"wp-image-6676\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/qu\u1ea3ng-c\u00e1o-\u0110i\u1ec7n-M\u00e1y-Xanh-_cover-1024x573.png 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/qu\u1ea3ng-c\u00e1o-\u0110i\u1ec7n-M\u00e1y-Xanh-_cover-300x168.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/qu\u1ea3ng-c\u00e1o-\u0110i\u1ec7n-M\u00e1y-Xanh-_cover-768x429.png 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/qu\u1ea3ng-c\u00e1o-\u0110i\u1ec7n-M\u00e1y-Xanh-_cover.png 1100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Video_Motion_Graphic\"><\/span><strong>Video Motion Graphic<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Motion graphics hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3 h\u1ecda chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng, l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khi d\u00f9ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3 h\u1ecda. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a m\u00e1y vi t\u00ednh, v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng&#8230; nh\u1eb1m chuy\u1ec3n t\u1ea3i n\u1ed9i dung m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c <strong>xu h\u01b0\u1edbng video marketing m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i hi\u1ec7n nay<\/strong> v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y l\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed kh\u00f4ng cao, d\u1ec5 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 n\u1ed9i dung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1ea3i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c quan.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/\u1ea3nh-\u0111\u1ea1i-di\u1ec7n-5-1140x641-1-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Video Motion Graphic\" class=\"wp-image-6677\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/\u1ea3nh-\u0111\u1ea1i-di\u1ec7n-5-1140x641-1-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/\u1ea3nh-\u0111\u1ea1i-di\u1ec7n-5-1140x641-1-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/\u1ea3nh-\u0111\u1ea1i-di\u1ec7n-5-1140x641-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/\u1ea3nh-\u0111\u1ea1i-di\u1ec7n-5-1140x641-1.jpg 1140w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Video_phim_ngan\"><\/span><strong>Video <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nhung-luu-y-khi-lam-phim-ngan.html\/\">phim ng\u1eafn<\/a><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea1ng video qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o l\u00e0 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng video marketing \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. L\u1ea5y n\u1ed9i dung v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n h\u00e0m ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh ti\u1ebft, chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ea7n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o. Video s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn, chia s\u1ebb h\u01a1n nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 lan t\u1ecfa v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem.\\<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"504\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/1